fields.product_description:
Lipp is a platform to connect startup founders and venture capitalists. We want to build strong connections between startup founders and VCs. or startup founders, Lipp can help to present your product and company very well.
  For venture capitalists, we offer a list of amazing startups, which you can find good ones to invest.
  There are a lot of opportunities of investments in the world.
  There are also a lot of people who could not take any investment because they are lack of information, because of their genders and prejudices. We think focusing to the product is the first and the most important thing. We are building an environment for the fairness and equality so that anyone who have a good idea can present their products and take investments!
fields.background:
1. Discrimination

There's a discrimination that men prefer to invest in companies run by other men. With men making up 90% of VCs, that preference is a bottleneck that keeps women out of the ranks of tech entrepreneurs. Pitching is not focused on the product but founders, sometimes.

2. Imbalance of information/education
Since investment and pitching process is mainly processed in offline, it is not easy to get a chance to get an investment. 
Someone never get education how to write a good portfolio or IRs to take investments. Even worse, if a founder is a woman in developer country, for an instance, they rarely have a chance to get feedbacks from venture capitalists or peers even they wrote a good portfolio.

References are listed:

https://www.caltech.edu/about/news/female-tech-entrepreneurs-hampered-bias-among-male-investors-study-finds-80420

fields.solution:
We connect between founders of startups and venture capitalists with Lipp.

For startups,

1. Offer guidelines to write a good portfolio

We do offer guidelines for startup founders to present themselves well with helpful links and videos so that anyone can make their own portfolio!

2. Feedback
For whom rarely have a chance to get feedbacks from investors or peers, we do offer feedback system so that they can make up for the weak points by receiving feedback before pitching or release.


For investors,

1. Let investors focus only on the project

We do list features of product at first. We do not offer any information that can cause discrimination such as name and gender. 

2. Portfolios in one place
Every portfolios and startups are listed in public. You can watch startups you are interested in by saving it in your list.

3. Get information of the industrial on easy way

We do offer a list of articles related to each product or company so that even investors who do not have enough information about the industrial can get understand more easily. Related articles are crawled automatically based on the category of the product.
